  "body": "<center>\n<h1 id=\"allure-emoji-pack\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5a2f302e0ab4d578084e6b3004bf22e36b152742.png\" alt=\"Allure Emoji Pack\"></h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-emoji-pack\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8a2dd1324a19f7594a6e032659b78fb3e5e89a2d.png\" alt=\"Modrinth\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/allure-emoji-pack/\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/48f3ed3f11e619ef7fea93c4344ae8f4ba233cb0.png\" alt=\"Planet Minecraft\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/p4ncake\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1fab8f2e1518ab9f6373586085d9aa785e0e3b9d.png\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-Fi\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/C9Q6XFG8T8\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6f5a8b8552da877af71a331499e3fffcb57b513a.png\" alt=\"Join our Community on Discord!\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p><h2><u><b>If you ever plan on using these emojis on your own project (for example a Minecraft server), you MUST contact me through my <a href=\"https://discord.gg/C9Q6XFG8T8\">Discord Server</a> and buy a license!</b></u></h2><strong>Allure Emoji Pack</strong> aims to replace the unifont emoji designs with actual pixel-consistent custom-made designs! The pack will only support single character Unicode emojis for now, because that's what the Minecraft font system supports.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/mh6HfOTP/images/ec898d7175ea7ed180c72a1865e05f192abc3566.png\" alt=\"All Currently Available Emojis\"></p>  \n<hr>\n<p><br>Please also check out <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-pack/\">Allure</a>, you might enjoy it! If you want to get notified for updates on the pack progress, give me suggestions or you wanna report any bugs, consider joining my Discord server <a href=\"https://discord.gg/C9Q6XFG8T8\">here</a>!</p>\n<br><br><hr>\n<h1>Other Projects!</h1>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-pack\"><img alt=\"Allure 3D Plants\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ab67244910ef4ab4fca79d7e98f4f7afbe9a75ec.webp\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-3d-plants\"><img alt=\"Allure 3D Plants\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a46651adb88e91abf37823d73fa1b42f66d4b596.webp\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-dark-theme-gui\"><img alt=\"Allure Dark Theme GUI\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f8deee765f891b6ca092c2ae5c120c8ea01c9007.webp\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-fresh-animations-support\"><img alt=\"Allure Fresh Animations Support\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a4b12553ad59462994b06b9f7124fd36c9a81138.webp\"></a>\n</center>",
